New York Rangers Clinch NHL Playoff Berth After Carolina Hurricanes Lose

-- B y   N a n c y   K e r c h e v a l
-- 
2011-04-10T01:34:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-10/new-york-rangers-clinch-nhl-playoff-berth-after-carolina-hurricanes-lose.html
The  New York Rangers  clinched a
National Hockey League playoff berth after the Carolina
Hurricanes lost to the Tampa Bay Lightning 6-2 in their final
regular-season game.  The Rangers secured the eighth and final playoff position
in the Eastern Conference. Earlier today,  New York  beat the New
Jersey Devils 5-2 at Madison Square Garden.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nancy Kercheval at 
 nkercheval@bloomberg.net  